{"tid":1219181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 數碼暴龍］日本示威者 撐 香港人：「你們是被時代選中的細路！」","createTime":"2019-06-13T18:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T13:37:05.000Z","uid":226548,"like":118,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"de569ff7ffb116cd28ba98147862be7e3a427f87","tid":1219181,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:16:34.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》修訂爭議在香港不斷升溫，就在示威者與警方發生衝突之後的周四（13日），日本東京亦有人在澀谷舉行集會，反對港府修訂《逃犯條例》。根據神奈川新聞的報道，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當晚約有2500人參與集會。</span></strong>有在場人士表示大約有三分一為香港在日留學生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2911825/org/5ade384b3ac3423b6de47749022b35b9.png/_5BnpF1o2dSIfw0mK6xDCu0Nk8-9HCD9txpkz7caZM8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2911825%2Forg%2F5ade384b3ac3423b6de47749022b35b9.png%2F_5BnpF1o2dSIfw0mK6xDCu0Nk8-9HCD9txpkz7caZM8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=cc79c5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本社運人士現場以粵語為香港集氣，「香港加油」。（讀者Kit Chan提供）<br />\n<br />\n不少日本學生代表在集會中發言，聲援香港人反對《逃犯條例》修訂。當中有一位自稱為宅男的日本學生熱血地表示，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">年輕的一代應當站出來，因為「你地係被時代選中嘅細路」。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ebaf8dbdbd6a183212c1247178c44cacfd94a8f3","tid":1219181,"uid":226548,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:18:38.000Z","msg":"活動疑由日本大學院生、27歲的元山仁士郎發起，下午5點30分至6時30分在香港駐東京經濟貿易辦事處前舉行；其後在晚間9點至10點，於澀谷JR站前再次舉行集會。在Twitter上已有不少日本人以 #TOKYOantiLAB發帖支援。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2911823/org/c5c714447b3181f75590fc53390eda9e.png/01mDfk0uoIV5gI7_YE4srBrEBqUxin36muqv8Jrqr_A?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2911823%2Forg%2Fc5c714447b3181f75590fc53390eda9e.png%2F01mDfk0uoIV5gI7_YE4srBrEBqUxin36muqv8Jrqr_A%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e6d61d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本社運代表：我哋係被時代選中嘅細路<br />\n<br />\n除了發起人元山仁士郎之外，亦有不少日本學運人士參與。26歲的奧田愛基自言是一個宅男，認識一些一樣喜歡《數碼暴龍》的香港朋友，他認為年輕一代應該站出來承擔責任，並<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">引用《數碼暴龍》名句：「我哋係被時代選中嘅細路」。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5baeba925162ef304dfd2ed9db9854b6e061e340","tid":1219181,"uid":201752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:20:22.000Z","msg":"想多謝佢哋可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5798d16e4f6eaaf7ceb5082fbcc085e7f63f4b72","tid":1219181,"uid":226548,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:20:53.000Z","msg":"參與集會的華人學生Kit Chan接受《香港01》訪問時表示，活動期間大會曾讓港人舉手，現場大約有三分一為港人在日留學生，其餘還有當地人及台灣留學生。有日本社運人士使用粵語「香港加油」呼喊口號；<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">集會最後亦有香港留學生上台齊唱《海闊天空》。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2911826/org/35122821359b7086e3fce5c7ab0b10b6.png/AfemSO5iX3Qqyke68svbRKIT8Dc2af18p0Bk-KdAZPg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2911826%2Forg%2F35122821359b7086e3fce5c7ab0b10b6.png%2FAfemSO5iX3Qqyke68svbRKIT8Dc2af18p0Bk-KdAZPg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=a58067ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據神奈川新聞報道，是次集會大約有2500人參加。（讀者Kit Chan提供）"},{"pid":"133969db09351258ee1d2e495af37e23e02e4a81","tid":1219181,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5baeba925162ef304dfd2ed9db9854b6e061e340","tid":1219181,"uid":201752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:20:22.000Z","msg":"想多謝佢哋可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:22:52.000Z","msg":"上呢個twitter (好似係）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/tasaki_kanagawa/status/1139169560534241280?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1139169560534241280&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F340143%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25BA%25AC2500%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2581%25B2%